1
00:01:29,650 --> 00:01:33,090
[Cage of Shadows]

2
00:01:33,610 --> 00:01:36,229
[Episode 10]

3
00:01:37,080 --> 00:01:39,039
Although we just met not long ago,

4
00:01:39,509 --> 00:01:40,350
we share

5
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:42,550
the same desire to survive.

6
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:43,240
Spill it.

7
00:01:43,240 --> 00:01:44,300
What's the matter?

8
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:45,979
I'm just trying to tell you

9
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:48,570
that there is a mole among us.

10
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:49,640
Who is it?

11
00:01:50,270 --> 00:01:52,200
I'm not entirely sure who it is yet,

12
00:01:52,520 --> 00:01:54,180
but I have a way to find her out.

13
00:01:54,600 --> 00:01:55,580
Why should I believe you?

14
00:01:55,580 --> 00:01:57,240
Giving it a try won't harm you.

15
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:59,580
The thing is, if we don't root her out,

16
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:01,190
we might all be doomed

17
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,700
in tomorrow's death match.

18
00:02:32,550 --> 00:02:33,470
Miss Nan,

19
00:02:33,490 --> 00:02:34,770
you're so smart.

20
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,360
Wan,

21
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,360
how about we just skip the talk?

22
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:41,520
For once, I finally had the mood to play
a guessing game with you girls.

23
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,720
Little did I expect

24
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,760
my identity would be revealed so soon.

25
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:46,560
You do know how to enjoy yourself,

26
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:48,760
Lord Voice-Keeper,
for joining a death match yourself.

27
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:51,290
I wonder if you will jump
into the den of snakes

28
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:52,920
the same when you lose?

29
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:54,120
Guards!

30
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,640
Hold on.

31
00:03:03,990 --> 00:03:06,920
Just now, you claimed to bet the lives

32
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:09,940
of all the female prisoners here
on the third round.

33
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:11,670
Are you aware

34
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,640
how high the stakes are?

35
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,140
Our plan is to take a gamble.

36
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,200
Fine.

37
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,030
Then tell me.

38
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,640
How do you want to proceed

39
00:03:40,790 --> 00:03:41,840
with the third round?

40
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,400
Both of us will each roll a dice and guess

41
00:03:43,400 --> 00:03:45,120
the other's number after the dices land.

42
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,440
Whoever guesses correctly wins.

43
00:03:46,440 --> 00:03:47,770
One game decides it all.

44
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:48,960
What do you say?

45
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:49,720
I agree.

46
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,480
Let's do as you said.

47
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:07,800
This is the third round
of the current death match.

48
00:04:08,660 --> 00:04:09,540
Ladies,

49
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:11,280
please get ready.

50
00:04:15,460 --> 00:04:16,320
If Miss Nan loses,

51
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,959
we'll have to die with her.

52
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,519
If you're that worried,

53
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:21,120
go play the game yourselves.

54
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,690
Will Yanzhi win?

55
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:23,960
Stop with this.

56
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:24,800
No more rubbing.

57
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:26,520
My palms are already sweating.

58
00:04:26,520 --> 00:04:28,120
Ladies, get ready.

59
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:31,280
The final round of this death match

60
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:33,420
begins now.

61
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:18,250
If the plan can be carried out at the end,

62
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:20,640
I hope you will help me with your ability
to tell dice numbers

63
00:05:20,640 --> 00:05:21,280
by sound.

64
00:05:22,090 --> 00:05:23,350
Why should I help you?

65
00:05:23,630 --> 00:05:26,090
You also long to leave this place,
don't you?

66
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,600
I suppose it takes more than

67
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:30,200
an individual's effort
to win the voice-keeper.

68
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,600
Only by working together

69
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:33,180
do we stand a chance of victory.

70
00:05:33,180 --> 00:05:34,470
We are hardly friends.

71
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:37,200
Why would you trust me?

72
00:05:37,390 --> 00:05:39,030
We will be friends after this.

73
00:05:39,030 --> 00:05:41,030
I firmly believe we will all get out

74
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,159
of here at last.

75
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,420
After I identify the dice number,

76
00:05:45,420 --> 00:05:48,030
I'll tell you what it is
by blinking my eyes.

77
00:06:27,760 --> 00:06:28,560
Sorry.

78
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,340
I guess the number of your dice...

79
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:40,680
is one.

80
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,640
What now?

81
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:57,280
Have you lost your ability to speak
like the mute servant?

82
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:59,120
She already waived her turn to guess.

83
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:01,250
Why don't you announce the result now?

84
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:11,030
The winner of the third round

85
00:08:11,210 --> 00:08:12,620
is Nan Yanzhi.

86
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,320
Take them down!

87
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,200
What?

88
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:31,370
Are you going back on your word now?

89
00:08:33,950 --> 00:08:34,750
Wan,

90
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,520
you could've defeated her.

91
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:38,400
Why did you deliberately let her go?

92
00:08:38,400 --> 00:08:39,679
To err is human.

93
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:43,600
I misheard her dice this time.

94
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:48,440
But I've never seen you err before.

95
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:57,260
Does this have something to do
with Zhuang Wujiu again?

96
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:03,680
Wan,

97
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,400
previously, you were deceived by her

98
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:06,660
and made a grave mistake already.

99
00:09:06,660 --> 00:09:08,680
How could you recklessly believe her again

100
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:10,280
and take one more wrong step?

101
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,720
We must not break

102
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,720
the rules of death matchs.

103
00:09:25,210 --> 00:09:26,870
But have you thought about...

104
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:35,880
Zan,

105
00:09:37,990 --> 00:09:39,520
I've made up my mind.

106
00:09:59,930 --> 00:10:02,600
It never occurred to me
that the great Lord Voice-Keeper

107
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,400
would break her word.

108
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,400
It's impossible to let you

109
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,530
take everyone away.

110
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,880
However,

111
00:10:10,650 --> 00:10:12,810
we can give you some gold

112
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,840
so you can reach the fourth floor

113
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,160
effortlessly.

114
00:10:20,350 --> 00:10:22,350
I must take all the girls away.

115
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,360
Don't push your luck!

116
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:25,080
Zan,

117
00:10:26,210 --> 00:10:27,280
please leave the room.

118
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,650
I'd like a word with her in private.

119
00:10:28,650 --> 00:10:29,060
Wan...

120
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,410
I'm asking you to leave.

121
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:40,680
Tell me.

122
00:10:41,250 --> 00:10:43,000
Why do you insist on
taking all the girls with you

123
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,270
and refuse to leave by yourself?

124
00:10:44,270 --> 00:10:46,070
Because I've made them a promise

125
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,660
that I'd get them out of here with me.

126
00:10:47,660 --> 00:10:48,400
What did you just say?

127
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,440
A promise?

128
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:51,200
Ha-ha.

129
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:56,660
You don't actually believe
that sort of stuff, do you?

130
00:10:57,640 --> 00:10:58,520
Why wouldn't I?

131
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:02,240
The night is still young.

132
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:03,320
How about...

133
00:11:03,800 --> 00:11:05,560
I tell you a story?

134
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,600
Ten years ago,

135
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,330
in the Moon House,

136
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:13,880
there was a famous courtesan
with unmatched pipa skills in the capital.

137
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:14,880
Coincidentally,

138
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,680
she was also called Ms. Kou.

139
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:19,630
All I seek in my life

140
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,130
is to spend every day

141
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:24,170
playing musical instruments with you
harmoniously

142
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,800
like this.

143
00:11:28,140 --> 00:11:29,940
May our happiness last forever.

144
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:33,200
May our bond never fade from memory.

145
00:11:39,410 --> 00:11:41,360
Blessed to be with a beauty like you,

146
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,890
I promise to stay committed

147
00:11:43,060 --> 00:11:44,410
to you for a lifetime.

148
00:11:44,610 --> 00:11:45,930
Hearing your words,

149
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:47,720
I feel

150
00:11:49,310 --> 00:11:50,160
so fortunate.

151
00:11:56,310 --> 00:11:57,450
Ms. Kou!

152
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:58,480
Mr. Xie...

153
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:00,620
Mr. Xie was taken by the authorities!

154
00:12:03,170 --> 00:12:04,370
How did that happen?

155
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:05,410
Mr. Xie is said to be

156
00:12:05,410 --> 00:12:08,040
engaged in the rebellion
conspired by Prince Xu and his aides.

157
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:10,370
Prince Xu's matter involves many people.

158
00:12:10,420 --> 00:12:11,810
I must rescue Xie.

159
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:18,760
Take these.

160
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:24,080
If the money is still not enough,

161
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:24,640
then...

162
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:34,700
Then pawn this pipa.

163
00:12:34,730 --> 00:12:35,530
Ms. Kou,

164
00:12:35,650 --> 00:12:36,710
this red sandalwood pipa

165
00:12:36,710 --> 00:12:38,280
is your most precious possession.

166
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:40,340
What pipa will you use if this is gone?

167
00:12:40,790 --> 00:12:42,990
There's no time to worry about that now.

168
00:12:43,460 --> 00:12:45,060
-Do as I said and go.
-Kou Wan!

169
00:12:54,410 --> 00:12:56,030
We're ordered to arrest Kou Wan,
an accomplice

170
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:57,360
to a rebel surnamed Xie.

171
00:12:57,710 --> 00:13:00,110
Ms. Kou, you'll have to go with us.

